      <title>南海紧张局势下东盟峰会聚焦海上安全和贸易</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/asean-summit-focus-maritime-security-trade-amid-south-china-sea-tensions-2024-03-06/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[澳大利亚总理安东尼·阿尔巴内斯周三表示，随着北京寻求加强其在有争议的南海的存在，海上安全、贸易和清洁能源将塑造该国与东盟的未来。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/asean-summit-focus-maritime-security-trade-amid-south-china-sea-tensions-2024-03-06/</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 06 Mar 2024 00:23:46 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>世界银行表示，太平洋岛屿面临增长放缓的挑战</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/pacific-islands-face-challenges-growth-slows-says-world-bank-2024-03-05/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[世界银行周三表示，太平洋岛国经济增长去年放缓至 5.5%，一些国家的旅游业和海外工人的汇款有所复苏，而飓风和干旱的冲击则阻碍了其他国家的发展。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/pacific-islands-face-challenges-growth-slows-says-world-bank-2024-03-05/</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 05 Mar 2024 23:23:08 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>经过三个月的宽松后，韩国 2 月份通胀加速</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/south-korea-inflation-quickens-february-after-three-months-easing-2024-03-05/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[周三官方数据显示，经过三个月的宽松后，韩国二月份消费者通胀加速，且快于市场预期。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/south-korea-inflation-quickens-february-after-three-months-easing-2024-03-05/</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 05 Mar 2024 23:19:20 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
